{"tid":1729731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[有高清圖]示威者在理工大學校園 A Core 附近被警方發射的布袋彈擊中下巴位置，登時皮開肉裂。","createTime":"2019-11-17T10:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T17:35:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e12e210cebab799d60fca62eab779b96795b08d","tid":1729731,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:36:11.000Z","msg":"據恒大編委報道，今日下午近5時，一名示威者在理工大學校園 A Core 附近被警方發射的布袋彈擊中下巴位置，登時皮開肉裂。救護員即時為他縫上四針。<br />\n<br />\n據警方行動報告，布袋彈屬較高程度武力，應向下肢瞄射。按國際使用守則，一般要求以較長距離發射。<br />\n<br />\n圖片素材來源：香港恒生大學編輯委員會<br />\nSource: 立場Facebook <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZvCxtj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZvCxtj.jpg&h=fa9e3bec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4c8b8a48b62324ac2e745e8f13343b1e9758c70","tid":1729731,"uid":48178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483cd40c30b59b2aacde7a6817b7ebdf4ec8918d","tid":1729731,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4c8b8a48b62324ac2e745e8f13343b1e9758c70","tid":1729731,"uid":48178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"希望佢唔會毁容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1823ddfe429854cb9a10e71400125bf2d58221ec","tid":1729731,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人有最新update?"},{"pid":"0306a3ec9bcf3dc93c4479b21d40348268660fc9","tid":1729731,"uid":73621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"43eb3d9fca7c0a3ef268d576401862c6cc42ddb0","tid":1729731,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit